    def print_event(event):
    event.plot("ortho")
    print("-------------------------------------")
    print(event[0])
    print("-------------------------------------")
    print(event[0].origins[0])
    print("-------------------------------------")
    print(event[0].magnitudes[0])
    print("-------------------------------------")
    try:
        print(event[0].amplitudes[0])
    except:
        pass
    print(event[0].picks[0])
    print("-------------------------------------")
    print(event[0].origins[0].arrivals[0])
    print("=====================================")
